❄️ Nordheim ​

Documentation relating to the spooni_nordheim.

🛒 Buy Now📍 View on Map

1. Installation ​

spooni_nordheim works Standalone.

To install spooni_nordheim:

  • Download the resource
    • On Cfx.re Portal
  • Drag and drop the resource into your resources folder
    • spooni_nordheim
    • spooni_nordheim_script
  • Add this ensure in your server.cfg
      ensure spooni_nordheim
  ensure spooni_nordheim_script
  • Now you can configure and translate the script as you like
    • config.lua
  • At the end, restart the server

If you have any problems, you can always open a ticket in the Spooni Discord.

2. For developers ​
